</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">docker logs n8n-postgres-1
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>
